Class DNode<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • orderGenerator.DNode<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - : Represents the data type (Message in this program)

    public class DNode<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class implementation of the node of the generic double linked list. Each node contains three elements:data and two pointers, one to the next node and the other to the previous node. Class also includes constructors for initialising the node, functions to check for the next node, deleting the next node etc.

    Aniket
